snippet.title: Who is He: Let Me Out - Chapter 1 Gameplay (Indonesian Horror Game)
snippet.description:
In this video we are playing a chapter 1 of third person Indonesian Horror Game Called Who is He: Let Me Out. Share your thoughts, leave a comment also Subscribe. #WhoisHeLetMeOut  #mystery #IndonesianHorror



A third person mystery puzzle game where you play as Alvin, a kid who trapped in a village. All you can do is run, hide, and solve the puzzles that block your path and get out of the village to find out who is responsible for everything that happened. 

------------------------------------------
PS4 PRO
PC Specs:  
CPU: Intel Core i7 8700K 
Motherboard: Gigabyte z370 gaming 3 
Memory: Corsair Vengeance LPX Black 16GB DDR4 
SSD: Samsung SSD 970 EVO NVMe M.2 
Graphics card: Zotac RTX 2080Ti
Operating System: Windows 10 
Monitor: LG 4K 
------------------------------------------
